{"tid":2092484,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"HKUE獲國際認可 只須3.5年畢業","createTime":"2020-07-03T08:44:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T16:57:12.000Z","uid":225931,"like":1,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b62c8a4a949ab803252ba26f349c3f2491ce3bfa","tid":2092484,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkue.edu.hk/upload/images/banner/20170612113910_60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkue.edu.hk%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Fbanner%2F20170612113910_60.jpg&h=53f44fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現今社會訊息萬變、競爭愈趨激烈。過去，一張大學畢業證書已是求職的最佳保證，今天卻變成一張基本的入場券。現今的雇主除注重員工的學歷外，更著重其積極性、自學精神及危機應變的能力。眾所周知香港的「填鴨式」教育制度，偏重書本上的知識及分數的高低，相對忽略考生的分析能力、應用能力及學習態度的建立。有見及此，HKUE於2005年引入外國的教學模式及升學系統，回應社會的需要。<br />\n<br />\n只需用3年半的時間便可完成整個學位課程，比在本地升學的學生早半年畢業。HKUE 採用澳洲的升學模式，修讀高級文憑只需20個月，而<span style=\"color: red;\">學士課程則需18個月</span>，加上 Melbourne Polytechnic 及 TAFE SA 的課程與澳洲大學的學士學位課程銜接度高，絕大部份的高級文憑的畢業生也能直接入讀學士學位課程，獲得學士的資格。<br />\n<br />\n課程以教授行業知識及技能為主，內容緊貼社會及業界的狀況和需要，更使用大量實例和個案分析授課，讓同學進行討論。同時，學員也能透過實習、模擬訓練、參觀活動及年宵攤位製作等，實踐理論，掌握行業所需的技能，提升競爭力，使他們畢業後能迅速就業。<br />\n<br />\n所有學歷(證書、高級文憑及學士學位)均由<span style=\"color: red;\">外國院校直接頒發</span>，獲國際性及業界的認可。我們的合作夥伴墨爾本理工學院及南澳專科技術學院，是全澳洲最大型的政府專上理工學院及技術學院，所頒發的學歷得到澳洲所有大學、美國、國際大學聯盟(IUA)和英聯邦國家認可。塔斯馬尼亞大學更在澳洲大學中位居前茅，持續被澳洲高等教育品質保證委員會評鑑為高級等級的學府。"},{"pid":"08dbaa3a2b3ba09789965d5d3638a412d3045b36","tid":2092484,"uid":38904,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:45:14.000Z","msg":"終極學店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d80dd77f65ce0360fa4ca586d521ff70de73eb","tid":2092484,"uid":27210,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:46:34.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">HKU</span><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">E</span>"},{"pid":"9c6df30225fafd7cb75eb3ae025be5b2d27f8e6d","tid":2092484,"uid":285514,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:49:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F28%2F092910_0945a33dc73f80a70d6e8af305acab60.jpg&amp;h=609b4d89&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"66a1a4c2d9e16cbbcfbce4586b6ccbf57fbb7c90","tid":2092484,"uid":285514,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T15:48:05.000Z","msg":"得 #1 係 1正評，後面啲留言全部 1負評<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nHKUE唔夠打手咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wfc2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852999fc9369fc053936e395d0782763de3bd2ba","tid":2092484,"uid":129042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-04T00:10:54.000Z","msg":"咁都信嘅真係要驗智商"},{"pid":"239915cf299b29383bf2cfb8fa234b0e4004b4db","tid":2092484,"uid":7828,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:11:55.000Z","msg":"騙徒Crystal Li李婉瑩新電話號碼: 91570141<br />\n<br />\n呢個騙徒係大陸人，由汕尾移民落黎香港，專呃d DSE 學生去報冇資歷級別 (HKQF) 嘅課程，另外會呃女性去美容院 <br />\n<br />\n更多資訊： <br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3D62kedb7g&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=f936cb9a\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=62kedb7g</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstories.hkjunkcall.com%2F%3Fd%3Di4waqbjt&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=caaa4fea\" target=\"_blank\">https://stories.hkjunkcall.com/?d=i4waqbjt</a> <br />\n<br />\n除咗美容，仲有SELL 教育，中醫，脫毛，投資等等<br />\n<br />\nChampion Team 另一成員 <br />\n如果去見工會見到佢 <br />\n(與Sam Chau Wing Sum 周詠森，Hugo Wong 及 三金合作） <br />\n<br />\n行業：教育及美容傳銷 <br />\n花名：Crystal Li / 水晶梨 <br />\n中文全名：李婉瑩 <br />\n英文全名：Li Wan Ying <br />\n常用工作電話：91570141（Updated) <br />\n另一工作電話：51610763 (可以 iMessage) <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f44ohbs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff44ohbs.jpg&h=a018e3ae&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1VbXiY9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1VbXiY9.jpg&h=a59da781&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ModKJqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FModKJqQ.jpg&h=a38f4662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係佢部分冇p圖嘅真樣<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yOkHOCZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyOkHOCZ.jpg&h=f279000e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3mSK1X0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3mSK1X0.jpg&h=be2c20d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以下係條女部分聲音 Backup <br />\n<br />\n同人plan 升學路線? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-14-23-56-24&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=983cf454\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-24</a> <br />\n<br />\n想叫我個fd上去 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-30\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-14-23-56-30&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=4cfe5b2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-30</a> <br />\n<br />\n番工幫到人? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-31\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-14-23-56-31&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=c3a67439\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-14-23-56-31</a> <br />\n<br />\n幫DSE 學生? <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-07-23-12-36-35\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-07-23-12-36-35&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=2c204435\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-07-23-12-36-35</a> <br />\n<br />\n自稱讀電影v1 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-07-28-22-04-03\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-07-28-22-04-03&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=7c9dfcc1\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-07-28-22-04-03</a> <br />\n<br />\n自稱讀電影v2 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-01-13-50-24\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-01-13-50-24&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=c2befc2d\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-01-13-50-24</a> <br />\n<br />\n無端端講美容 v1 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-21-23-45-56\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-21-23-45-56&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=b27b60bd\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-21-23-45-56</a> <br />\n<br />\n無端端講美容 v2 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-21-23-45-56-1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-21-23-45-56-1&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=13833e81\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-21-23-45-56-1</a> <br />\n<br />\n無端端講美容 v3 <br />\n<a href=\"https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-21-23-45-53\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsoundcloud.com%2Ffff-lll-957348350%2Faudio-2019-08-21-23-45-53&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=6dd0f921\" target=\"_blank\">https://soundcloud.com/fff-lll-957348350/audio-2019-08-21-23-45-53</a>"},{"pid":"ec4f6cbc013ae799cda17b266660c23537010b12","tid":2092484,"uid":7828,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:13:06.000Z","msg":"各位DSE學生報讀任何課程前，請先查詢有關課程是否有<span style=\"color: green;\">HKQF（香港資歷架構）</span>的認可，切勿因為一時大意誤信他人被騙。<br />\n<br />\n資歷名冊官網<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Findex.html&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=f6d28927\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/index.html</a><br />\n<br />\n資歷搜尋<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkqr.gov.hk%2FHKQRPRD%2Fweb%2Fhkqr-tc%2Fsearch%2Fqr-search%2F&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=05d04fa4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hkqr.gov.hk/HKQRPRD/web/hkqr-tc/search/qr-search/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基本上傳銷或者詐騙的人，他們喜歡先入為主，不停感情勒索，裝作大家感情深厚<br />\n<br />\n帶你去見工：<br />\n「要為屋企人著想，賺多啲錢」<br />\n「讀大學冇用㗎，呢份工先有錢途」<br />\n「有錢途再追逐自己夢想都唔遲」<br />\n「好自私，只顧及讀書，真係好好好自私，錢又媽比，家境又5好，明知讀完得萬幾蚊，照顧5到屋企，你又讀得5勁，點解要讀？」<br />\n「問你要揀買樓定讀大學，又問你憑咩講話冇時間讀書（因為平時有出黎發夢）<br />\n<br />\n帶你去傳銷學校 ：<br />\n「我想你改變自己」<br />\n「唔好輕易放棄，放棄自己將來」<br />\n「ive/副學士/hd 冇用㗎」<br />\n「想識d有上進心嘅男仔」<br />\n「d顧問好嚴格，記得帶齊所有身份證明文件/證書」<br />\n「張證書有poly 認可㗎，你讀其他之後出嚟做嘢冇用點算」<br />\n（poly 你老母，打過去poly 話唔撚係，只係出席活動的證書，唔會有咩學歷證明，食屎啦臭雞)<br />\n<br />\n帶你去美容：<br />\n「我帶你去做facial呀/你陪我去做facial呀」<br />\n「我當你是朋友才給你這優惠」<br />\n<br />\n[轉貼］<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[搵工要小心，切勿中美容教育傳銷陷阱]  大學生小心職場陷阱</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164225%2Fpage%2F1&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=0f9715e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164225/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n透過 HKG 分享一則貼文：[大學生小心職場陷阱] 小心有傳銷公司成員係交友app 扮係你朋友<br />\n<a href=\"https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fforum.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7164242%2Fpage%2F1&d=nCDZGLdcAmB0c2Oxl6asXNHbQOt8JOG57pMmRaSdLYE%3D&h=0c82839c\" target=\"_blank\">https://forum.hkgolden.com/thread/7164242/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n叫你去interview個個聲稱人工係每單Job計 每單job有4位數字，Interview個個就話係計人頭 教育同醫美都唔同計法，前後矛盾<br />\n<br />\n教育分 1-5 6-30 31-465 （重有再上<br />\n1-5:$1000/1<br />\n6-30:$1800/1<br />\n31-465:$2400/1<br />\n<br />\n醫美就計%<br />\n<br />\n佢地聲稱自己唔會由個客手上拎錢<br />\n係客比錢pr公司搵到嘅合作機構<br />\n再由合作機構比返佣pr即係佢地<br />\n<br />\n中匯商業大廈18-20樓<br />\n19樓主要做interview / training，18/20樓好似係office<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2020/02/15/hcjw3E.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2020%2F02%2F15%2Fhcjw3E.png&h=fba48af3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yZVcOmK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyZVcOmK.jpg&h=8e48423a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dHYehe4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdHYehe4.jpg&h=72537123&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"126099f69cf2514c84a1e4359c2e5f09680c3802","tid":2092484,"uid":329324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b62c8a4a949ab803252ba26f349c3f2491ce3bfa","tid":2092484,"uid":225931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T08:44:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.hkue.edu.hk/upload/images/banner/20170612113910_60.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.hkue.edu.hk%2Fupload%2Fimages%2Fbanner%2F20170612113910_60.jpg&h=53f44fd3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n現今社會訊息萬變、競爭愈趨激烈。過去，一張大學畢業證書已是求職的最佳保證，今天卻變成一張基本的入場券。現今的雇主除注重員工的學歷外，更著重其積極性、自學精神及危機應變的能力。眾所周知香港的「填鴨式」教育制度，偏重書本上的知識及分數的高低，相對忽略考生的分析能力、應用能力及學習態度的建立。有見及此，HKUE於2005年引入外國的教學模式及升學系統，回應社會的需要。<br />\n<br />\n只需用3年半的時間便可完成整個學位課程，比在本地升學的學生早半年畢業。HKUE 採用澳洲的升學模式，修讀高級文憑只需20個月，而<span style=\"color: red;\">學士課程則需18個月</span>，加上 Melbourne Polytechnic 及 TAFE SA 的課程與澳洲大學的學士學位課程銜接度高，絕大部份的高級文憑的畢業生也能直接入讀學士學位課程，獲得學士的資格。<br />\n<br />\n課程以教授行業知識及技能為主，內容緊貼社會及業界的狀況和需要，更使用大量實例和個案分析授課，讓同學進行討論。同時，學員也能透過實習、模擬訓練、參觀活動及年宵攤位製作等，實踐理論，掌握行業所需的技能，提升競爭力，使他們畢業後能迅速就業。<br />\n<br />\n所有學歷(證書、高級文憑及學士學位)均由<span style=\"color: red;\">外國院校直接頒發</span>，獲國際性及業界的認可。我們的合作夥伴墨爾本理工學院及南澳專科技術學院，是全澳洲最大型的政府專上理工學院及技術學院，所頒發的學歷得到澳洲所有大學、美國、國際大學聯盟(IUA)和英聯邦國家認可。塔斯馬尼亞大學更在澳洲大學中位居前茅，持續被澳洲高等教育品質保證委員會評鑑為高級等級的學府。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T01:23:39.000Z","msg":"呃人呃到好似車志健咁款真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7b0fe9c38271b476dd2788264b3f16ed45cd6c9","tid":2092484,"uid":362494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T16:57:12.000Z","msg":"讀完就後悔一生<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呃人讀埋呢垃圾課程<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}